<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:14:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于全球需求强劲，5 月份亚洲工厂活动有所扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的私人调查显示，随着制造商受益于全球需求的扩大，亚洲工厂活动在 5 月份有所扩大，这增加了该地区经济持续复苏的希望，而中国正在显示出反弹的早期迹象。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟专员表示，欧盟提议的俄罗斯液化天然气转运禁令不会给亚洲带来任何问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧盟能源委员卡德里·西姆森周一在东京对记者表示，针对俄罗斯液化天然气（LNG）转运的欧洲新制裁提议不太可能影响亚洲买家。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度莫迪计划大选后改革以与中国制造业竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</link><description>据两名知情政府官员透露，如果印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪本周赢得第三个任期，他计划采取一系列有利于商业的措施，包括推动制定法规，使雇用和解雇工人变得更容易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动增速创两年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，中国5月份制造业活动以两年来最快速度增长，生产和新订单强劲，表明该行业在产业政策支持下依然强劲。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀报告公布后，货币走势谨慎，关注欧洲央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</link><description>货币市场本周开局谨慎，周一美元小幅走低，此前上周数据显示美国通胀在 4 月份企稳，为美联储在今年晚些时候降息打开了大门。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因降息承诺和工厂回升而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</link><description>亚洲股市周一上涨，因为投资者期待欧洲（很可能还有加拿大）降息，作为全球政策宽松的下一步，尽管粘性通胀可能会使这一过程变得漫长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 00:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国称英国军情六处将两名中国政府工作人员变成间谍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-britains-mi6-turned-two-chinese-govt-staff-spies-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国国家安全部周一在一份声明中表示，中国指控英国秘密情报局军情六处将两名未透露姓名的中国中央国家机关工作人员变成英国政府的间谍。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-britains-mi6-turned-two-chinese-govt-staff-spies-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>尽管市场复苏，繁文缛节仍阻碍中国境外IPO管道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/red-tape-clogs-chinas-offshore-ipo-pipeline-even-markets-recover-2024-06-02/</link><description>银行家、中国公司高管及其投资者表示，他们预计今年离岸IPO荒将持续，在经济放缓的情况下影响企业筹集资金的能力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/red-tape-clogs-chinas-offshore-ipo-pipeline-even-markets-recover-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：PMI盛典开启新月，聚焦中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 21:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>据天空电视台报道，时装公司 Shein 将在伦敦提交 500 亿英镑的 IPO 招股说明书</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-fashion-giant-shein-file-prospectus-50-billion-london-float-sky-news-2024-06-02/</link><description>据天空新闻周日报道，在线时尚公司 Shein 正准备在伦敦上市之前向英国金融行为监管局提交招股说明书，以供批准，该公司的估值可能约为 500 亿英镑（合 637 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 19:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-fashion-giant-shein-file-prospectus-50-billion-london-float-sky-news-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>Nvidia表示下一代AI芯片平台将于2026年推出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-says-its-next-generation-ai-chip-platform-be-rolled-out-2026-2024-06-02/</link><description>Nvidia 首席执行官黄仁勋周日表示，该公司的下一代人工智能 (AI) 芯片平台名为 Rubin，将于 2026 年推出。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-says-its-next-generation-ai-chip-platform-be-rolled-out-2026-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗外交部就海湾群岛问题召见中国驻德黑兰大使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-ministry-summons-chinese-ambassador-tehran-over-gulf-islands-2024-06-02/</link><description>据伊朗官方媒体周日报道，伊朗外交部已召见中国驻德黑兰大使，抗议中国与阿联酋就伊朗对阿联酋也声称拥有主权的三个岛屿的主权发表的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 10:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-ministry-summons-chinese-ambassador-tehran-over-gulf-islands-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾人员在争议海域用枪指着中国海警</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-personnel-pointed-guns-chinese-coast-guard-disputed-waters-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国官方媒体周日称，上个月，一艘菲律宾船只上的人员在南海争议海域用枪指着中国海警。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 07:32:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-personnel-pointed-guns-chinese-coast-guard-disputed-waters-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>泽伦斯基主导亚洲安全会议，中国和台湾贸易倒刺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-dominates-asia-security-conference-china-taiwan-trade-barbs-2024-06-02/</link><description>泽连斯基在新闻发布会上表示，他未能在会议上会见中国代表团，并对北京不出席峰会感到失望。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 06:43:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-dominates-asia-security-conference-china-taiwan-trade-barbs-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚寻求与中国进行军事会谈并与菲律宾建立关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-seeks-military-talks-with-china-ties-with-philippines-2024-06-02/</link><description>副总理理查德·马勒斯周日在香格里拉对话安全峰会上表示，澳大利亚已要求与中国进行军事会谈，并愿意与菲律宾走得更近。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 05:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-seeks-military-talks-with-china-ties-with-philippines-2024-06-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>